&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The story of &amp;ldquo;Happy Island Fantasy&amp;rdquo; takes place on an almost isolated island. Ron came here on a treasure ship to explore the treasures in the ancient miracles and met several beauties on the island. You will complete a happy and exciting journey on this island.​&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
